 a hot surface, the evolution of the shape of the drop, temperature,\nand vapor mass fraction were predicted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2017 16:29:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2017 04:25:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
