Delta\\equiv V_H^{1/4} <f.$ To have such a well defined origin and hierarchy\nof scales in inflationary models is not common. We use this property of HNI to\ndetermine bounds for the inflationary energy scale $\\Delta$ and for the\ntensor-to-scalar ratio $r$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2017 18:56:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Nov 2017 22:59:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
